    "FSDP/autograd overhead is visible but below the attention+MORI branches in this trace: record_param_comms 6.87s median, RegisterPostBackwardFunctionBackward 5.97s, MmBackward0 5.61s, fsdp::chunk_cat 4.28s, and c10d::barrier 3.69s.",
    "The next optimization ladder should therefore keep fused owner-rank MoE backward first, but put dense-fallback attention backward replacement/avoidance next, ahead of broad FSDP wrapper surgery."
  ],
